600
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:51,390
Young Master.

601
00:33:51,390 --> 00:33:52,740
You can't believe him.

602
00:33:52,780 --> 00:33:53,980
It must have been him.

603
00:33:58,990 --> 00:33:59,920
Li, don't worry.

604
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:02,770
No matter who the murderer is,

605
00:34:03,350 --> 00:34:04,350
we need evidence.

606
00:34:07,380 --> 00:34:08,710
If you are the murderer,

607
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:10,719
I will avenge Happy.

608
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:16,610
I'll give you a chance now.

609
00:34:17,870 --> 00:34:19,000
Who is the murderer?

610
00:34:21,020 --> 00:34:22,150
I really don't know.

611
00:34:23,260 --> 00:34:25,460
But a servant being killed for no reason

612
00:34:25,719 --> 00:34:28,150
is merely a lead-in.

613
00:34:29,020 --> 00:34:30,880
But as long as we follow this trail

614
00:34:31,020 --> 00:34:32,020
and keep looking,

615
00:34:32,909 --> 00:34:36,150
