768
00:41:08,150 --> 00:41:09,750
Something really happened.

769
00:41:10,200 --> 00:41:11,040
It was a ghost.

770
00:41:11,310 --> 00:41:12,620
The blood footprints led towards the second floor.

771
00:41:12,620 --> 00:41:13,700
We all saw it.

772
00:41:14,250 --> 00:41:15,250
Don't be nervous.

773
00:41:15,380 --> 00:41:16,980
You can't believe in ghosts.

774
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:18,480
Who else

775
00:41:18,890 --> 00:41:21,020
