777
00:41:23,860 --> 00:41:24,980
It's strange.

778
00:41:25,610 --> 00:41:27,320
How was Yu Qiushuang killed?

779
00:41:27,620 --> 00:41:29,900
How was she sealed in the escort box?

780
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:32,360
